article.description: — Josh Earley had 16 points in Southeast Missouri State's 52-47 victory against SIU Edwardsville on Saturday night.
article.headline: Earley scores 16 to lead Southeast Missouri State over SIU Edwardsville 52-47
article.linkText: Earley scores 16 to lead Southeast Missouri State over SIU Edwardsville 52-47
article.story: CAPE GIRARDEAU, Mo. -- — Josh Earley had 16 points in Southeast Missouri State's 52-47 victory against SIU Edwardsville on Saturday night. Earley had eight rebounds for the Redhawks (7-12, 2-4 Ohio Valley Conference). Rob Martin scored 10 points while finishing 5 of 10 from the floor, and added five assists. Damarco Minor finished with 21 points for the Cougars (11-9, 4-3). Shamar Wright added 15 points and six rebounds. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
